{"tid":2029213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Google：已修正搜尋器 搜「黃色」即彈「黃色經濟圈」","createTime":"2020-05-22T06:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T06:55:22.000Z","uid":28765,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7481e6c0239447f93f4fbcc0844ddfa41ba62b","tid":2029213,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"今日較早時，網民發現Google搜尋「藍色」，會自動提供相關關鍵字，排行第一位的，為「藍色經濟圈」。不過搜尋「黃色」，甚至是「黃色經濟」，都沒有彈出任何相關字，外界因此質疑Google是否「自閹」。<br />\n<br />\n本報就此向Google查詢，Google最新指出：「Google 對於預測查詢字串（Autocomplete）有清晰的政策規定，禁止包含煽情露骨、粗俗或不雅內容，但演算法未必每次拿捏準確，我們在知悉相關情況後已檢視，並已經作出修正。」本報亦再次測試搜尋「黃色」，的確成功彈出預測查詢字串，而排行第一位的為「黃色經濟圈」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/fxb9WidKqphlxoQbr3nJhB_Agw0=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/SB3FJYBTIXAW3J56B3OJIIH33A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Ffxb9WidKqphlxoQbr3nJhB_Agw0%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FSB3FJYBTIXAW3J56B3OJIIH33A.png&h=1f09d5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200521/2XIAO56JPYK2MV5RP3KEUUAT7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200521%2F2XIAO56JPYK2MV5RP3KEUUAT7Y%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSpR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=72fdb1ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200521%2F2XIAO56JPYK2MV5RP3KEUUAT7Y%2F&h=3c057b51\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200521/2XIAO56JPYK2MV5RP3KEUUAT7Y/</a>"},{"pid":"1723f6f1b47e70ad56341d9cfe43c2deebf40bd1","tid":2029213,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b164e31e857014fc5ed429b225a5dc8550e407e","tid":2029213,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:43:38.000Z","msg":"扮乜撚野呀GOOGLE   擺明籠裡雞  引紅色員工入關  偷偷比支拿改撚左啦"},{"pid":"03c8f08f13c55961de733ec50132223892ff5898","tid":2029213,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"唔奶共啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebbb780fc26f07c744ea50e3e47eef684132a7a","tid":2029213,"uid":209248,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奶完又奶吹咩<br />\n<br />\n佢獨家"},{"pid":"525708af06c97a3c4f2b81576c307660f5c5ea55","tid":2029213,"uid":258968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"彈出黃色經濟圈係因為你之前search過<br />\n<br />\n紫色字.."},{"pid":"9f20926329a34b5d32294240eeb11d99d3759a47","tid":2029213,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"525708af06c97a3c4f2b81576c307660f5c5ea55","tid":2029213,"uid":258968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"彈出黃色經濟圈係因為你之前search過<br />\n<br />\n紫色字.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:50:32.000Z","msg":"你自己試下"},{"pid":"e21432efbcb4b7810f04d79eaa64024271f78992","tid":2029213,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ebbb780fc26f07c744ea50e3e47eef684132a7a","tid":2029213,"uid":209248,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奶完又奶吹咩<br />\n<br />\n佢獨家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:50:48.000Z","msg":"點奶都唔會俾你入大陸市場㗎啦<br />\n窿閪google"},{"pid":"460f4f5ad6941ef7dde8a747b62bf3d401803edc","tid